### Index of metrics endpoints (JSON)
GET {{host}}/api/metrics
Accept: application/json

### Index of metrics endpoints (HTML)
GET {{host}}/api/metrics
Accept: text/html

### Get entity counts
GET {{host}}/api/metrics/counts
Accept: application/json

### Get coverage of reviews/details over index
GET {{host}}/api/metrics/coverage
Accept: application/json

### Get reviews summary (aggregates and freshness)
GET {{host}}/api/metrics/reviews/summary
Accept: application/json

### Get details breakdown (free/paid, platforms)
GET {{host}}/api/metrics/details/breakdown
Accept: application/json

### Get picks summary (days, latest)
GET {{host}}/api/metrics/picks/summary
Accept: application/json

### Get configured bucket labels (game metadata)
GET {{host}}/api/metrics/thresholds
Accept: application/json


